text:
عيد ميلاد سعيد لاميرة عزيزي تشين 
حبيبي تشين في هذا اليوم من العام السابق ولدت اميرتك اتذكر في يوم و لادتها حدث رعد و برق كثيرا في بلدي و الممتع هي قوتك في اكسو 
قريبا من هذا اليوم سوف اذهب الى مدينة النجف الاشرف لزيارة امير المؤمنين الامام علي بن ابي طالب( ع) لادعو لك و لاميرتك ان تبقوا بصحة جيدة و ان تعود بسلامة و امان من التجنيد 
اشتاق اليك كثيرا الى حد غير متوقع في كل ثانية تمر اتذكر ابتسامتك و صوتك و جمالك و كلماتك المؤثرة عندما تعود سوف يكون من اسعد ايامي و سوف انتظره طوال الوقت الى ذلك الحين اتمنى ان تبقى بخير دوما 
مهما اصبح الانتظار ممتعا فانه الحب( قائد اكسو المثالي ) 
Happy birthday to dear Princess Chen 
My love, Chen, on this day of the previous year, your princess was born. I remember one day when she gave birth to a lot of thunder and lightning in my country, and the joy is your strength in EXO
Soon from this day, I will go to the holy city of Najaf to visit the Commander of the Faithful, Imam Ali bin Abi Talib (peace be upon him). I will invite you and your princess to remain in good health and to return safely and safely from conscription
I miss you so much, unexpectedly. Every second that passes I remember your smile, voice, beauty and touching words. When you return, it will be one of my happiest days, and I will wait for it all the time until then I hope you stay fine always 
No matter how enjoyable waiting becomes, it is love (The ideal EXO Commander)

author: @gasanalizap.5981
text:
Dear my dear Chen,

오랜만이에요. 잘 지내시나요?
내가 이 편지를 쓰는 이유를 방황하고 있지 않나요? 많이 보고싶어요.
지난 몇 달 동안, 우리는 많은 흥망성쇠를 경험했습니다. 하지만 좋고 아름다운 일도 일어납니다. 잘 지내고 있죠? 부인과 아기는 어때요? 당신은 행복합니까? 당신이 행복하다면 나도 행복해요.

사실 이런 일은 한 번도 해본 적이 없어서 정말 뭐라고 해야 할지 모르겠어요. 나는 단지 지금 당신이 얼마나 그리운지 표현하고 싶을 뿐이에요. 며칠 전부터 당신의 음악을 듣고 있었어요. 그러다 오늘 감정에 젖었어요. 왜 그런지 모르겠어요, 하지만 나는 당신이 크게 웃고 모든 것에 징징대는 모습을 보고 싶어요. 내가 미쳤나 봐요? 하하하하하

아무튼 10시가 다 되어갑니다. 밥 먹었어요? 당신은 지금 아기를 돌보고 있나요? 그녀는 아름답습니까? (물론이죠!) 나는 당신의 아기를 볼 수 있어서 흥분됩니다 헤헤헤헤 그녀는 당신을 닮았나요? (물론이죠..?) 하하하하하 


편지가 너무 오래간 것 같아요 하하하하하
P.S. 네이버 파파고를 이용해서 쓰고 있어요. 다 맞는지 모르겠네요 (하지만 나는 그것이 그렇기를 바랍니다 하하하하하) 떨려요. 알아요, 당신이 이걸 읽을 확률은 0.001%밖에 없어요 (난 상관없어) 

P.P.S. 몸조심하세요. 좋은 음식을 많이 드세요. 아내와 아기를 잘 돌보세요. 그들에게 건강에 좋은 음식을 많이 주세요. 첸 아빠 사랑해요 하하하하하 (I can't believe I just calle you daddy! 하하하하하)

잘자요!

author: @sheela6855
text:
Letter from a dandelion,
           It's been long since we have heard about you. Hope you are good. Hope you are healthy and taking good care. And hope you are happy.

You said right that you and our members are the tree and we are their leaves. Jongdae remember that we are always there. Always there to cherish your happiness, always there during your ups and downs.

 kim jongdae, you know what? Seeing you growing, your progress and now transforming into a man, witnessing all these makes me feel like a proud mom. (Tho, i'm younger)
Jongdae you are doing great. We believe that you will be a great father and obviously our boys will be the best uncles. I can imagine how much the baby is going to be loved. Indeed the baby is a blessing. 
Jongdae, remember that whatever descision you take, we respect you and your descisions regardless of what is it. Chennie, thankyouu for being an artist carrying millions of hearts. Thankyou for singing and making us relax. Thankyou for interacting with us through your music. 

And also,
To the baby, 
In the next 10, 15 years...you will start to know the things around you....dear baby, you will be very proud to know how great is your father. Love him like he lovess youu okay? And also remember that he has called you a "blessing". Your dad has been our youth.
You have a blessed family. ❤

Sending lotsssss of love. <3 ❤

author: @diyapathak4014
text:
Honestly, Chen deserves a lot more recognition. He deserves the world, actually. He's always so underrated and it infuriates me.

Now prepare yourself because I'm gonna rant a freaking lot because this precious human is just so underrated. Let's list most of his aspects deserving to be fangirled about, shall we?

1.) AN UNDERRATED VISUAL: Jongdae often gets pushed to the side in case of visuals among so many members who're gorgeous themselves. Most of exo-l' notice Baekhyun's simultaneous cuteness and hotness, Kyungsoo's voice and acting, Suho's charm and endearing awkward sides, Xiumin's cute and sexy af sides, Kai's sexiness and shyness, Sehun's booty and just plain boldness, Chanyeol's talented and silly self and Yixing's dance and just plain adorably lost behaviour. Somehow in noticing these, they fail to notice Chen or better yet Kim Jongdae. Because while Chen is his stage personality, what we should notice is who Jongdae is. And let me tell you, that guy is all of above qualities wrapped up in one with an unimaginable amount of kindness and gentleness. He's such a beautiful guy with those high cheekbones and kitty smile. He's one of the few kpop idols who can rock all the hairstyles, especially WITHOUT any fringe.

2.) KINDEST EXO MEMBER:
Even the members have acknowledged the fact that Jongdae is the kindest member to ever exist. He's often found massaging the neck and shoulders of his members after a particularly tiring concert/practice. They've announced Jongdae as the umma because, and I quote "He takes care of all the members so well". When any EXO member had to attend a concert while being injured, Jongdae has always spent all the time of concert making that member feel included. In EXO's Showtime, during the haunted house incident, he took hot packs to all the staff members who were disguised as ghosts in such cold weather. At the end of the episode he even thanked them.
He's the member that has earned himself the nickname of " Fansign boyfriend" because of the unique way he treats his fans by always maintaining eye contact and giving them all a warm smile because he knows how much that moment matters to the fans.

3.) ONE OF THE POLITEST PEOPLE TO EVER GRACE THIS EARTH: Even Kyungsoo has acknowledged the fact that Jongdae is gentle and polite. On every reality show or interview, he always makes sure to thank the staff and his thank you speeches after winning an award always include the line about thanking all the people who've ever helped EXO. He always entertains his group members whenever they ask him to do something. He's always extra polite and kind to MC's and takes all their joking jabs and teasing taunts with a smile on his face.

4.) HIS VOCALS!!!!! : If you know anything about EXO, you'd know that Jongdae is one of the best voices in Kpop industry. His ability to transition between low and high notes, maintaining the fluency and rhythm perfectly makes him so precious to EXO. Not to mention he's a great songwriter. EXO's three songs including 'She's dreaming...' were written by him.

5.) HIS PLAYFUL PERSONALITY: As a member of beagle line, Jongdae has acknowledged that he's much more playful with other members than those out of the beagle line. He tries to keep the mood lighthearted, even on the expense of his pride. He'll gladly be silly in order yo cheer other members right up. Along with Bakehyun, he's the mood maker of the group.

6.) A HARD WORKER: Every EXO member has said that Jongdae isn't a great dancer like Kai or Lay, but still when you watch any of their MV's, you won't be able to believe that fact. Yes, he wasn't born with dance talent but he has worked damn hard and you can literally see that in every dance performance he gives. Even Baekhyun has said that one of the things that changed the most about Jongdae is his dancing.

7.) A MODEST PERSON: No matter how many times he's complimented on his singing skills, he always gets shy and thanks the person sincerely. Whenever members are discussing the best visual or dancer, he's the one to sit quietly on the side and observe them, with a smile on his face. He never seeks attention about his singing skills or looks. On the other hand he compliments all the members on their skills, making sure to encourage and motivate them.

8.) HE'S KIM JONGDAE: All the above things constitute to this fact. The fact that we should never forget is that while Chen is great, with his model looks, angelic voice and sexy dancing; Jongdae is just as precious with his playful comebacks, his adorable whines, and his kindness. Kim Jongdae is one of the best people on this planet who has never been arrogant and always helps charities in his free time. He's the one that always has a smile on his face and will tell his feelings honestly but still make sure to not burden other members with his issues.

What I'd like to say to him is that he should always know that he'll always have us. No matter what happens, we'll always support him and although some may forget him in front of other members who are more vocal, there are always people who'll be thankful for him being just him. Thanks a lot for letting us know the beautiful person that Jongdae is.
